I didn't do it.

24
00:01:50,235 --> 00:01:51,694
I didn't do it either.

25
00:01:51,778 --> 00:01:53,613
Whatever. Don't worry about it.

26
00:01:53,696 --> 00:01:58,076
It made hanging out with my friends

27
