566
00:42:00,726 --> 00:42:01,560
NJ!

567
00:42:03,187 --> 00:42:04,647
Gosh.

568
00:42:23,374 --> 00:42:25,084
GO-OH, NU-A

569
00:42:25,167 --> 00:42:26,669
Hello, Ms. Kook.

570
00:42:26,752 --> 00:42:28,462
It must have been a long day.

571
00:42:28,545 --> 00:42:30,422
